e and industrial grade salt products. In addition, the company trades in various chemicals, such as sodium tripolyphosphate, sodium lignosulfonate, PVC resin, titanium dioxide, citric acid, EVA, zircon flour and sand, kaolin clay, and borax pentahydrate. It sells its products under the i-FLO, and Sapan brands. The company was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Noida, India."}}